Step 1: Install Required Packages & Necessary Binaries

Step 2: Install the packages on both worker nodes:

  CMD: sudo apt-get -y install socat conntrack ipset

  Packages :- conntrack:  Manages connection tracking in Linux Kernal load balancing & NAT
              ipset    : Creates & manage IP set for fast IP lookup Network polices & firewall Rule
              libipset3: 
              socat    : Used in kubenetes for Port forwarding & exposing localhost services via TCP Proxies

